    <briefdescription>
<para>System that synchronizes TransformComponents with SceneNodes. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This system bridges the gameplay simulation and the rendering scene graph. It propagates local transformations from dirty TransformComponents to their corresponding SceneNodes, triggers a scene graph update, and then reads back the computed world transforms into the TransformComponents. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
